That's actually quite a good question, RideTheCrash. I usually keep a Tab open in Firefox. Or bookmark the page in Firefox.

Some people still need to learn how great it is if you have bookmarkfolders ON your toolbar in Firefox, next to the Home button etc., that way you can have one named "torrents" and it will pulldown when you click it. Really handy for short-term bookmarking.
